data.description:
2504 Leland Avenue, Akron, OH 44312 WELCOME HOME! Inviting 2-story Colonial Home in the heart of Ellet for ease of traveling to the local eateries & cool coffee shop 2 blocks away & near the hiking trail & community center as well as grocery stores, hardware store and plenty more! Great big yard and even bigger with the vacant lot next door which that lot IS a buildable lot for an additional single-family home or purchase to have a huge, fenced yard! The current Owner says it is a quiet area with very friendly and quiet neighbors and always feels safe at the property! Gorgeous steel blue premium color siding installed ion the exterior in 2023 and the electric panel was replaced in 2022 as well as the stove was new in 2022. The main floor has a large Living Room with picture windows in the front for plenty of natural light, dining room area that can hold a full length dining table with ample seating complete with sliding glass patio door to the rear covered porch for grilling and entertaining, the well designed kitchen layout with gas stove, side by side stainless steel refrigerator freezer, dishwasher and above the stove microwave with exhaust to the exterior! The 1st floor is rounded out by a pantry, half bath and side entry door. The 2nd floor houses all 3 bedrooms including the primary bedroom with door from the bedroom in to the full bathroom. Plenty of closet space and natural light in the bedrooms. The lower level is partially finished as well as having plentiful storage. Basement has rough plumbing for a full bath with shower id Buyer wants to have a 2nd bath, easy to finish. There is a high efficient furnace and air conditioning system for your comfort. The concrete driveway is a bonus with plenty of parking for all of your toys and vehicles and a storage shed for all of the yard fun accessories. The home is being sold as is and for the Buyer's protection, a home warranty will cover the home for the entire 1st year of home ownership!
Extra Lot MLS # 5014017
